        "### The Transfer Learning Pipeline\n",
        "Our strategy utilizes **Embedding Transfer**.\n",
        "1. **ANN**: Learns a basic semantic mapping.\n",
        "2. **CNN**: Refines the embedding to detect local n-gram patterns.\n",
        "3. **Transformer**: Adds global context awareness.\n",
        "4. **LSTM/GRU**: Incorporates sequential dependencies.\n",
        "\n",
        "By transferring the weights of the `embedding` layer at each step, we ensure that each new model starts with a highly sophisticated understanding of the vocabulary."
      ]
