        "---\n",
        "  ## Model 3 - Transformer Encoder\n",
        "  **Connected to CNN**: inherits CNN's refined embedding.\n",
        "  Multi-head self-attention captures global context and long-range token interactions.\n",
        "\n",
        "  `CNN embedding -> Transformer block (MHA + FFN) -> GlobalAvgPool -> Dense`"
