        "---\n",
        "  ## Model 4 - LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory)\n",
        "  **Connected to Transformer**: inherits the transformer's embedding (now even more sequence-aware).\n",
        "  Gating mechanisms resolve the vanishing gradient problem. Additive attention focuses on important tokens.\n",
        "\n",
        "  `Transformer embedding -> BiLSTM (stacked) -> AdditiveAttention -> Dense`"
      ]
    },
    {
