        "---\n",
        "  ## Model 5 — GRU (Gated Recurrent Unit)\n",
        "  **Connected to LSTM**: inherits the most refined embedding from the full chain.  \n",
        "  Lighter than LSTM with comparable power. Multi-Head Attention adds global context.\n",
        "\n",
        "  `LSTM embedding → BiGRU (stacked) → MultiHeadAttention → Residual → Dense`"
